{"tid":1348183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"〈支持〉民政局員工罷工","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:40:13.000Z","uid":106957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38f01c035bfce479bd8c76855ef19164adc7535b","tid":1348183,"uid":106957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVeuWjk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVeuWjk.png&h=9aeb6457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗白衣暴民隨街持武器打人，警方卻隻眼開隻眼閉未有執法，就連政府人員亦對警黑合作看不過眼，稱會罷工抗議。有市民在Facebook發帖，指「因政府無為，黑警合作，今日罷工，以示抗議」，hashtag為「不合作運動」、「民政事務局」，而帖文附有的相片可見，一辦公室內有人在分隔板上掛起紙皮，上述相關帖文內容，當中有「HAB」字樣，正是民政事務局英文縮寫。暫時未知有關人士是否公務員。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向民政事務局查詢是否有員工今天罷工抗議。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190722&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59849924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190722%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59849924&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=99a67736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190722%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59849924&h=67d49260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190722&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59849924</a>"}]}